<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.4">
<l>niṉaippāṉ pukilkaṭa lekkali ṉuṇmaṇa liṟpalar</l>
<l>eṉaittō rukaṅkaḷu mivvula kāṇṭu kaḻintavar</l>
<l>maṉaippāṉ maruṅkaṟa māytalal lāṉmaṟṟuk kaṇṭilam</l>
<l>paṉaittāṇ matakaḷi ṟaṭṭavaṉ pātam paṇimiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you enter into thinking, as many as the fine [grains of] sand in the dunes</l>
<l>are those who passed away after ruling this earth for however many yugas.</l>
<l>Other than [their] vanishing so that the traces of the parts of [their] houses are erased we don’t see.</l>
<l>Humble yourseselves at the feet of the one who killed the rutting elephant with bulging feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
